description: This file is a header file (.h) that declares exported function prototypes related to Web Authentication Server Object. It contains function declarations for creating, removing, enrolling objects, and initializing the Authso component.

methods.name: WebCreateAuthso
methods.description: Creates an instance of the Web Authentication Server Object, given container, owner, and reserved contexts.

methods.name: WebAuthsoCreate
methods.description: Constructs a Web Authentication Server Object with given contexts.

methods.name: WebAuthsoRemove
methods.description: Removes or destroys the Web Authentication Server Object.

methods.name: WebAuthsoEnrollObjects
methods.description: Enrolls or registers necessary objects within the Web Authentication Server Object.

methods.name: WebAuthsoInitialize
methods.description: Initializes the Web Authentication Server Object to a ready state.
